      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS MANAUDOU (1) continued her winning form with another strong run after leading to make it two in a row, scoring by 0.8 lengths (23.58) at this track over 407m. Won at her only start from this box. Expected to go well again. CAMBLA DIVA (3) has a strong record this journey with 10 wins and a minor from 13 starts. Scored by 3.5 lengths last time (29.81) in a Grade 5/6 over 510m at this track. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. REGAL WOLF (2) has a strong record this trip with 10 wins and eight placings from 26 starts. Was out of placings last time (24.31) at this track in a Free For All, finishing fifth and beaten 7 lengths. Can feature in the finish. ROXY CAMBLA (6) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
